liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Hello and welcome to the first Hottest 100 Like A Version live blog! My name's Velvet, I'm a certified Hottest 100 fanatic and I'm going to be joining you all through today's countdown from #100 to #1 But I'm not going it alone, I'll be joined by a few special guests that will pop in throughout the countdown: Madi Chwasta - Hottest 100 data journalist and analyst Kane Sutton - Hottest 100 digital producer We want to hear from you! Chuck us a comment on the live blog or have a chat with triple j on their official social channels. So, grab a bev and some snacks and settle in for the best covers the last 20 years has to offer!
